name: A Day Long Remembered
Lore: '''It has seen the end of Kenobi and will soon see the end of the Rebellion.''',
Text: 'If Obi-Wan not on table, deploy on Yavin 4 or Hoth system. If system ''Blown away,'' relocate to opponent''s side of table. Rebels and Rebel starships are deploy +8 and lost immunity to attrition. Canceled if Obi-Wan is deployed. (Immune to Alter.)',
